=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過諗諗下個僱主都無咩良心<br />\n3個月代通知金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d 工要半年通知添啦，你肯簽咪無問題囉"},{"pid":"6b992d9d9066efece105e2d592b0009b25c4873a","tid":496894,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔打去奴工處問<br />\n連登仔9UP就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪咁呀，大家手足"},{"pid":"3cbfbb394cc566440e1b55ab3d2c6660b75130e9","tid":496894,"uid":120850,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:06:01.000Z","msg":"點解唔問勞記走黎問厚德村"},{"pid":"350c83c2d6cdbbf2cdb3426e289636e7fcc02f6b","tid":496894,"uid":21120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"唔係同屋企人簽果刻已經輸左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前幾年又係去做1對1 都係同屋企人簽"},{"pid":"3356d3e514f06fa71fb2ac61d57b89b43d9c6741","tid":496894,"uid":92937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>份約係同公司㗎話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n非公司 私人打工</blockquote><br />\n屌<br />\n你返返下工死撚左<br />\n唔通你僱主又可以同你老豆老母拎代通知金咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大佬呀<br />\n做一對一私看護<br />\n對像10個有9個都隨時會死<br />\n咁唔保障員工<br />\n人工加通知金加埋10幾萬<br />\n<br />\n我建議所有有末期病患 每人請5個私人護士<br />\n反正死左無人要找數<br />\n10萬請個22歲靚女RN洗下屎眼<br />\n不知幾暢快</blockquote><br />\n你明知個僱主隨時會死<br />\n都唔加返個條款保障自己<br />\n咁係邊個on9先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如加咩條款可以保障到？<br />\n寫明死左要照出糧？<br />\n問題係而家個遺產管理人唔出<br />\n我係咪要同管理人簽埋約？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n薪金點都要出，返左幾多日就計日薪<br />\n代通知金就一定無嫁嗱<br />\n薪金唔出可以民事追討返"},{"pid":"6c060fa3b6b794231c913d2ab77b23a484bd40a8","tid":496894,"uid":46452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身同僱主簽左約 要三個月離職通知期<br />\n搞到我推左好多job <br />\n因為要唔撈要提早3個月通知<br />\n有d 靚offer 等唔到我咁耐 無奈放棄<br />\n因我唔想比3個月代通知金<br />\n早幾日僱主走左 我呢個post亦自然被解僱<br />\n僱主家人係咪都應該賠翻3個月代通知金比我？</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母你賣身俾一個人定係賣身俾一間公司架"},{"pid":"d3988628b3baeaa9ae0763e3ce02bf9d7febbca0","tid":496894,"uid":158936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:17:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cec4698bc8b94ce8964886de23dfc67ddc9df7a","tid":496894,"uid":20429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"你都痴撚線<br />\n如果調返轉係你暴斃<br />\n唔通僱主搵你老豆老母追返三個月代通知金啦喎？"},{"pid":"a80f2e84cce22264bf6c116aa98d4ce01f23826a","tid":496894,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"僱主已死！所有法律責任解除"},{"pid":"fb6b79480dd2eb4b6f4e60bdec78dc1809b82605","tid":496894,"uid":25204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>份約係同公司㗎話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n非公司 私人打工</blockquote><br />\n屌<br />\n你返返下工死撚左<br />\n唔通你僱主又可以同你老豆老母拎代通知金咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大佬呀<br />\n做一對一私看護<br />\n對像10個有9個都隨時會死<br />\n咁唔保障員工<br />\n人工加通知金加埋10幾萬<br />\n<br />\n我建議所有有末期病患 每人請5個私人護士<br />\n反正死左無人要找數<br />\n10萬請個22歲靚女RN洗下屎眼<br />\n不知幾暢快</blockquote><br />\n欸。唔通你就係廿二歲靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec6675f705290950ef25e405c6ae8bab971cdd3","tid":496894,"uid":97162,"